Vehement walked outside of the Brotherhood craft, followed by Sun Crusher and 
Reflector.  Dark One, followed by his four Oblitercons stepped up.

&quot;Welcome, Dark One.&quot; Vehement said with a smile.  Slag. Vehement thought.  
There would be no way to know his name if I just arrived on the planet! 

&quot;How do you know my name?&quot; the leader of the Oblitercons asked, turning to 
his troops.  &quot;Head back to base, except for Sixshot, Ares, and Double Punch.&quot;

The orders were followed out as the troops headed off.

&quot;Now answer my question.&quot;

&quot;Dark one is your name?  That&#39;s somewhat amusing.  I merely meant &#39;dark one&#39; 
as in the color of your body.&quot;

&quot;Oh, who are you?&quot;

&quot;I am Vehement.  Leader of this ship.&quot;

&quot;I am Dark One.  A soldier in the Alliance,&quot; Dark One said, though he was 
really just a mercenary, &quot;the leader of the Alliance is Zardus.  He is not 
here though.  He usually leads all major attacks personally, but we moved our 
base, so he is needed with our bases.&quot;

&quot;So, that is your base on the island.&quot;

&quot;...yes.&quot; Dark One hesitated.  &quot;What did that blasted KitKat want with you?&quot;

&quot;She wanted me to ally with her.  But now it seems she&#39;s much to weak to 
protect my forces if we got in a battle.&quot;

&quot;Heh.  Can&#39;t protect yourselves?&quot;

&quot;The robots you see in front of you are all that remain of us.  We got in a 
battle with three Maximal strike cruisers, and the rest were killed in the 
crash.&quot;

&quot;Blasted Maximals.  So, why should I let you live?&quot;

&quot;Though we have little cannon fodder value, we can produce energon from solar 
technology.  And weapons, and our base is quite strong.  With three bases at 
your disposal.  Though, I&#39;d like to remain neutral.&quot;

&quot;Interesting...I&#39;ll have to contact our leader.&quot; Dark One activated his comm. 
unit, setting the frequency to the inner monologue comm. unit in Zardus&#39; head.
&quot;Zardus, Dark One here.  KitKat&#39;s pathetic forces have retreated.  The leader 
of the base we are at, Vehement, wishes to discuss a peace treaty with us.&quot;
